                                        <div class="col-6 text-left">
                                            <h5><b>E & E ALL Disputes Are Subject To Salem Jurisdiction</b> </h5>  <br />
                                            <h5><b>Goods Once Sold Cannot Be Taken Back</b> </h5>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 text-right">
